title: The Ultimate Self-Sufficiency Handbook: A Complete Guide
description:
The Ultimate Self-Sufficiency Handbook: A Complete Guide to Baking, Crafts, 
Gardening, Preserving Your Harvest, Raising Animals and More by Abigail R. Gehring

Overview: This compact guide provides advice, tips, and step-by-step instructions for hundreds of projects, offering the entire family the tools they need to make the shift toward self-sufficient living. Readers will learn to dip candles, bake bread, make maple syrup, start a vineyard, and much more. With special features for young homesteaders, this is an essential family guide to self-sufficient living
